    ""Bet you can't see me, Lucy. Bet you can't."
    "the voice said again."
    "And Lucy saw through the shadows of the looming trees, two red pinpricks blinked like sinister stars."
    "I do. I see you." 
    "Lucy said and Lucy did."
    "And it was the last thing she ever saw."
    
